channel.title: MoparScape closes unexpectedly?
channel.description:
Ok this is weird. Whenever I go to www.moparisthebest.com and the applet begins to load, all of my internet browser windows suddenly close without warning.
Is anyone else getting this problem?
Does anyone know how to fix this?
P.S. I am using Mozilla Firefox
